; Proliferate development config.
; The @anyharness/sdk dependency uses a file: link for local co-development.
; When the SDK is published to npm, remove the file: override from package.json
; and use the published version instead.
;
; To use a sibling AnyHarness checkout during development:
;   1. Build the SDK: cd ../anyharness/sdk && pnpm build
;   2. The file: link in package.json will resolve to the built dist/
;
; For release builds, the published @anyharness/sdk version should be used.
